translation: Make your way toward the Cathedral.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Make your way toward the Cathedral.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Lancers!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Lancers!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Titan!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Titan!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Defeat the Golems!{#Name="説明文"}
source: Defeat the Golems!{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Enemy attack! Enemy attack!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Enemy attack! Enemy attack!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: All men, take position now!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: All men, take position now!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Stay strong! Don't let 'em through!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Stay strong! Don't let 'em through!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: We're the last line of defense...{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: We're the last line of defense...{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Full speed ahead! Move! We got you covered!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Full speed ahead! Move! We got you covered!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Here goes!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Here goes!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Incoming enemies reported!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Incoming enemies reported!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Understood. Locate and pursue!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Understood. Locate and pursue!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: May Lady One inherit the world!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: May Lady One inherit the world!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Victory to our leader!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Victory to our leader!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Protect our Intoner! Protect her until the end!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Protect our Intoner! Protect her until the end!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Charge! Full steam ahead!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Charge! Full steam ahead!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Are you serious?{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Are you serious?{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Of course I am! If not now, then when?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Of course I am! If not now, then when?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Th-That's Zero? She's...so...strong... {#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Th-That's Zero? She's...so...strong... {#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Hey! Stop mumbling and start fighting!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Hey! Stop mumbling and start fighting!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: It's kill or be killed here!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: It's kill or be killed here!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Ah... Aaaaahh! Yaaaahh!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Ah... Aaaaahh! Yaaaahh!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Any who can wield a weapon, follow me!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Any who can wield a weapon, follow me!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Wait! We can't leave the wounded behind!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Wait! We can't leave the wounded behind!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: We can and we will! Now charge!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: We can and we will! Now charge!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Keep attacking! We outnumber them!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Keep attacking! We outnumber them!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Sir, yes, sir!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Sir, yes, sir!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Remember who you fight for!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Remember who you fight for!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: You want that insane lord to return and oppress us again?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: You want that insane lord to return and oppress us again?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Lady One is the one true savior! For us and the world!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Lady One is the one true savior! For us and the world!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: We need to fall back!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: We need to fall back!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Never! We're charging through!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Never! We're charging through!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: B-But...{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: B-But...{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Our lives are expendable here! Now move! Forwaaaaard!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Our lives are expendable here! Now move! Forwaaaaard!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Zero! What should I do now?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero! What should I do now?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Support me from the air.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Support me from the air.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Uh...me?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Uh...me?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You see anyone else here who can fly?{#Name="Zero"}
source: You see anyone else here who can fly?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Good point! Guess I'm the best man for the job!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Good point! Guess I'm the best man for the job!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Th-There she is! We're under attack!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Th-There she is! We're under attack!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Stay calm! Give it all you got!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Stay calm! Give it all you got!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Don't let her set foot in the Cathedral!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Don't let her set foot in the Cathedral!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Yeah! Victory will be ours!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Yeah! Victory will be ours!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Retreat! Retreat!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Retreat! Retreat!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: There's nowhere to run! Stand and fight!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: There's nowhere to run! Stand and fight!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: ううむ……全員……突撃！{#Name="兵士Ａ"}
source: ううむ……全員……突撃！{#Name="兵士Ａ"}

translation: We'll never give Lady One over{LF}to these fiends! Never!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: We'll never give Lady One over{LF}to these fiends! Never!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Never!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Never!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Captain, your orders!?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Captain, your orders!?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Do whatever it takes! Just kill her!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Do whatever it takes! Just kill her!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: She must be stopped at all costs!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: She must be stopped at all costs!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Oh, come on now. More of them?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Oh, come on now. More of them?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Bring it on! I'll tear 'em limb from limb!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Bring it on! I'll tear 'em limb from limb!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Sounds like trivia time! Did you know{LF}"limb from limb" originally referred{LF}to trees and not body parts?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Sounds like trivia time! Did you know{LF}"limb from limb" originally referred{LF}to trees and not body parts?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Surprise, surprise. This brainless{LF}piece of shit again.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Surprise, surprise. This brainless{LF}piece of shit again.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Don't worry about me!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Don't worry about me!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You take that black piece of shit!{#Name="Zero"}
source: You take that black piece of shit!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: O-Okay!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: O-Okay!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: And get back safe!{#Name="Zero"}
source: And get back safe!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: {06}>{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: {06}>{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Y-You got it!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Y-You got it!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: よっ{#Name="ディト"}
source: よっ{#Name="ディト"}

translation: Man, this stupid dust is gettin'{LF}into all my cracks.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Man, this stupid dust is gettin'{LF}into all my cracks.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I'm gonna need a bath soon.{#Name="Dito"}
source: I'm gonna need a bath soon.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Whaddya say, Z? Wanna join me?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Whaddya say, Z? Wanna join me?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Maybe next time.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Maybe next time.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: ついに、ここまで！？{#Name="兵士Ｆ"}
source: ついに、ここまで！？{#Name="兵士Ｆ"}

translation: 全員、配置につけ！！{#Name="兵士Ａ"}
source: 全員、配置につけ！！{#Name="兵士Ａ"}

translation: 第二列突破されました！{#Name="兵士Ｇ"}
source: 第二列突破されました！{#Name="兵士Ｇ"}

translation: ひるむな！門を守れ！戦うのだ！{#Name="兵士Ｂ"}
source: ひるむな！門を守れ！戦うのだ！{#Name="兵士Ｂ"}

translation: やられた！後を頼む…{#Name="兵士Ｃ"}
source: やられた！後を頼む…{#Name="兵士Ｃ"}

translation: おい？起きろ！死ぬな！誰か救護班を！{#Name="兵士Ｄ"}
source: おい？起きろ！死ぬな！誰か救護班を！{#Name="兵士Ｄ"}

translation: 遅い！遅い！そんなんでワンを守れるのかっ？{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 遅い！遅い！そんなんでワンを守れるのかっ？{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ふほっ。敵兵総勃ちの出迎えでございますか{#Name="オクタ"}
source: ふほっ。敵兵総勃ちの出迎えでございますか{#Name="オクタ"}

translation: いいねー。誇りも希望もナニも全部へし折っちゃえ！ {#Name="ディト"}
source: いいねー。誇りも希望もナニも全部へし折っちゃえ！ {#Name="ディト"}

translation: 門の前にいるヤツらを一掃できれば…{#Name="デカート"}
source: 門の前にいるヤツらを一掃できれば…{#Name="デカート"}

translation: え。私、頼まれてますぅう？{#Name="セント"}
source: え。私、頼まれてますぅう？{#Name="セント"}

translation: まあ、私の腕と才能があれば、簡単ですけどぉお。土下座して頼むとか？そういうのは、ほら、もう、気持ちの問題だからぁああ{#Name="セント"}
source: まあ、私の腕と才能があれば、簡単ですけどぉお。土下座して頼むとか？そういうのは、ほら、もう、気持ちの問題だからぁああ{#Name="セント"}

translation: オクタ！頼みたいことがあるのだが{#Name="デカート"}
source: オクタ！頼みたいことがあるのだが{#Name="デカート"}

translation: あれ？無視？そんな照れなくていいんですけどぉお{#Name="セント"}
source: あれ？無視？そんな照れなくていいんですけどぉお{#Name="セント"}

translation: 死んだ？ねえねえ、死んだ？わっ。きったない死体！{#Name="ディト"}
source: 死んだ？ねえねえ、死んだ？わっ。きったない死体！{#Name="ディト"}

translation: 救護班呼ぶ前にさぁ、せっかくだから、オマエも死んどけば？{#Name="ディト"}
source: 救護班呼ぶ前にさぁ、せっかくだから、オマエも死んどけば？{#Name="ディト"}

translation: ディト…{#Name="デカート"}
source: ディト…{#Name="デカート"}

translation: The best dragon, at least.{#Name="Zero"}
source: The best dragon, at least.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero, you okay down there?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero, you okay down there?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I'm fine. Go take out that cannon for me.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I'm fine. Go take out that cannon for me.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You got it! You g—{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: You got it! You g—{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What's wrong?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What's wrong?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I didn't repeat, Zero! I didn't repeat myself!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I didn't repeat, Zero! I didn't repeat myself!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You just did, dummy.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You just did, dummy.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: This shit really is never gonna end, is it?{#Name="Zero"}
source: This shit really is never gonna end, is it?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh ho! Need someone to ease that tension?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho! Need someone to ease that tension?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: You're not helping, Octa!{#Name="Zero"}
source: You're not helping, Octa!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Look at these things. Fat, ugly freaks.{LF}I wish they'd never been born.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Look at these things. Fat, ugly freaks.{LF}I wish they'd never been born.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: That's a serious wish to make, Dito.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: That's a serious wish to make, Dito.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Whatever, Decadus. Sometimes I wish{LF}you'd never been born either!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Whatever, Decadus. Sometimes I wish{LF}you'd never been born either!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Nnngh... Such cruel words...{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Nnngh... Such cruel words...{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: All right, let's go.{#Name="Zero"}
source: All right, let's go.{#Name="Zero"}
